{"title_page": "1965\u201366 Liga Leumit", "text_new": "{{Infobox football league season\n|competition= [[Israeli Premier League|Liga Leumit]]\n|season=1965\u201366\n|winners=[[Hapoel Tel Aviv F.C.|Hapoel Tel Aviv]]<br />6th title\n|relegated= [[Maccabi Petah Tikva F.C.|Maccabi Petah Tikva]] <br> [[Beitar Tel Aviv F.C.|Beitar Tel Aviv]]\n|league topscorer= [[Moshe Romano]]<br>[[Mordechai Spiegler]] (17)\n|matches= \n|total goals= \n|prevseason=[[1964\u201365 Liga Leumit|1964\u201365]]\n|nextseason=[[1966\u201368 Liga Leumit|1966\u201368]]\n}}\n\nThe '''1965\u201366 [[Liga Leumit]] season''' saw [[Hapoel Tel Aviv F.C.|Hapoel Tel Aviv]] crowned champions and qualify for the first [[AFC Champions League|Asian Club Championships]]. [[Moshe Romano]] ([[Shimshon Tel Aviv F.C.|Shimshon Tel Aviv]]) and [[Mordechai Spiegler]] ([[Maccabi Netanya F.C.|Maccabi Netanya]]) were the joint top scorers with 17 goals each.\n\n[[Maccabi Petah Tikva F.C.|Maccabi Petah Tikva]] and [[Beitar Tel Aviv F.C.|Beitar Tel Aviv]] were [[Promotion and relegation|relegated]] to [[Liga Alef]].\n\n==Rule changes==\nPrior to the season the [[Israel Football Association|IFA]] decided to allow [[Substitute (association football)|substitutions]] of one player and one goalkeeper during matches.<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date=2 September 1965 |title=\u05db\u05dc \u05e7\u05d1\u05d5\u05e6\u05d4 \u05ea\u05ea\u05de\u05d5\u05d3\u05d3 \u05e4\u05e2\u05de\u05d9\u05d9\u05dd \u05ea\u05d5\u05da \u05e9\u05d1\u05d5\u05e2\u05d9\u05d9\u05dd \u05e0\u05d2\u05d3 \u05d0\u05d5\u05ea\u05d5 \u05d9\u05e8\u05d9\u05d1 - \u05d1\u05e2\u05d5\u05e0\u05ea \u05d4\u05db\u05d3\u05d5\u05e8\u05d2\u05dc \u05d4\u05d1\u05d0\u05d4 |trans-title=Each Team Would Compete Against the Same Opponent Within Two Weeks - In the Next Football Season |url=http://jpress.org.il/Olive/APA/NLI_heb/SharedView.Article.aspx?href=MAR%2F1965%2F09%2F02&id=Ar01907&sk=192EB353 |language=Hebrew |work=Ma'ariv |location=Tel Aviv |access-date=11 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Final table==\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=HTA|name_HTA=[[Hapoel Tel Aviv F.C.|Hapoel Tel Aviv]]\n|team2=MTA|name_MTA=[[Maccabi Tel Aviv F.C.|Maccabi Tel Aviv]]\n|team3=HPT|name_HPT=[[Hapoel Petah Tikva F.C.|Hapoel Petah Tikva]]\n|team4=MNE|name_MNE=[[Maccabi Netanya F.C.|Maccabi Netanya]]\n|team5=HPRG|name_HPRG=[[Hapoel Ramat Gan F.C.|Hapoel Ramat Gan]]\n|team6=STA|name_STA=[[Shimshon Tel Aviv F.C.|Shimshon Tel Aviv]]\n|team7=HHA|name_HHA=[[Hapoel Haifa F.C.|Hapoel Haifa]]\n|team8=HMY|name_HMY=[[Hapoel Mahane Yehuda F.C.|Hapoel Mahane Yehuda]]\n|team9=HKRG|name_HKRG=[[Hakoah Maccabi Amidar Ramat Gan F.C.|Hakoah Ramat Gan]]\n|team10=BnY|name_BnY=[[Bnei Yehuda Tel Aviv F.C.|Bnei Yehuda]]\n|team11=MJA|name_MJA=[[Maccabi Jaffa F.C.|Maccabi Jaffa]]\n|team12=HJE|name_HJE=[[Hapoel Jerusalem F.C.|Hapoel Jerusalem]]\n|team13=BRS|name_BRS=[[Hapoel Be'er Sheva F.C.|Hapoel Be'er Sheva]]\n|team14=MSH|name_MSH=[[Maccabi Sha'arayim F.C.|Maccabi Sha'arayim]]\n|team15=MPT|name_MPT=[[Maccabi Petah Tikva F.C.|Maccabi Petah Tikva]]\n|team16=BTA|name_BTA=[[Beitar Tel Aviv F.C.|Beitar Tel Aviv]]\n\n|win_HTA=12|draw_HTA=14|loss_HTA=4|gf_HTA=36|ga_HTA=23\n|win_MTA=14|draw_MTA=6|loss_MTA=10|gf_MTA=45|ga_MTA=29\n|win_HPT=10|draw_HPT=14|loss_HPT=6|gf_HPT=42|ga_HPT=29\n|win_MNE=13|draw_MNE=8|loss_MNE=9|gf_MNE=49|ga_MNE=35\n|win_HPRG=12|draw_HPRG=10|loss_HPRG=8|gf_HPRG=40|ga_HPRG=32\n|win_STA=12|draw_STA=8|loss_STA=10|gf_STA=37|ga_STA=31\n|win_HHA=12|draw_HHA=8|loss_HHA=10|gf_HHA=31|ga_HHA=32\n|win_HMY=11|draw_HMY=9|loss_HMY=10|gf_HMY=36|ga_HMY=38\n|win_HKRG=9|draw_HKRG=12|loss_HKRG=9|gf_HKRG=37|ga_HKRG=34\n|win_BnY=9|draw_BnY=10|loss_BnY=11|gf_BnY=31|ga_BnY=38\n|win_MJA=9|draw_MJA=10|loss_MJA=11|gf_MJA=33|ga_MJA=41\n|win_HJE=9|draw_HJE=10|loss_HJE=11|gf_HJE=29|ga_HJE=40\n|win_BRS=9|draw_BRS=9|loss_BRS=12|gf_BRS=21|ga_BRS=25\n|win_MSH=10|draw_MSH=7|loss_MSH=13|gf_MSH=33|ga_MSH=40\n|win_MPT=7|draw_MPT=9|loss