 Goldmember]]''\n| Mini-Me\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"APNewsObit\" />\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[Pauly Shore Is Dead]]''\n| Himself\n| \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Postal (film)|Postal]]''\n| Himself\n| \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[The Love Guru]]''\n| Coach Punch Cherkov\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"APNewsObit\" />\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[College (2008 film)|College]]''\n| Himself\n| \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"BFI\"/>\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''[[The Imaginarium of Doctor Parnassus]]''\n| Percy\n| \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[Keith Lemon: The Film]]''\n| Archimedes\n| \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"BFI\"/>\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Trailer Park Boys]]: Drunk, High, and Unemployed: Live in Austin''\n| Himself\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''Gnome Alone''\n| The Gnome\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"RT\">{{cite web|title=Verne Troyer|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/celebrity/verne_troyer|publisher=[[Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=April 22, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018 \n| ''The Delivery'' \n| The Boss \n| Short film, Posthumous release\n|\n|-\n|2019\n|''Aliens Clowns and Geeks''\n| Emperor Beezel-Chugg\n|Post-production, Posthumous Release; Final film role\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"AICN\" />\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Year(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\"| Role\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|References}}\n|-\n|1999\u20132000\n|''[[Shasta McNasty]]''\n|Verne\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n|2000\n|[[Jack of All Trades (TV series)|''Jack of All Trades'']]\n|[[Napoleon|Napoleon Bonaparte]]\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"TVG\" />\n|-\n|2002\n|[[Sabrina the Teena